At first I thought this was using a compiler to figure out data dependencies on regular javascript objects, including built in&#x27;s on the window and coming from third party dependencies, so you could do this:<p><pre><code>   &lt;div&gt;window width: {window.innerWidth}&lt;&#x2F;div&gt;
</code></pre>
But it&#x27;s not, it&#x27;s just on objects that subclass a Store.
